Package: enrichmeta
Title: Metabolite Enrichment Analysis Using KEGG Pathways
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("botao", "zhang", email = "3048986896@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Comprehensive toolkit for KEGG-based metabolite enrichment analysis and pathway visualization.
    Key features include:
    - Automated retrieval and caching of KEGG pathway data
    - Hypergeometric test-based metabolite set enrichment analysis
    - Pathway-metabolite mapping and annotation
    - Publication-quality visualization of enrichment results
    - Analysis of shared metabolites between pathways
    - Integration with KEGG REST API
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    KEGGREST,
    ggplot2,
    stringr,
    utils,
    stats,
    scales
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/maxgodson1/enrichmeta
BugReports: https://github.com/maxgodson1/enrichmeta/issues
SystemRequirements: libcurl
